FBIS4-22040 "jptot016__l94097" JPRS-TOT-94-016-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 15 April 1994 WEST EUROPE TURKEY Kurdish Rebel Leader Says Ready for Peaceful Settlement Kurdish Rebel Leader Says Ready for Peaceful Settlement NC1504121994 Paris AFP in English 1042 GMT 15 Apr 94 NC1504121994 Paris AFP English BFN [Excerpt] Istanbul, April 15 (AFP) - Kurdish rebel leader Abdullah Ocalan, who heads the Kurdistan Workers Party (PKK) fighting the Turkish government, said Friday he was ready to end a 10-year war against Ankara if favourable conditions for a peaceful solution were set up. He made the offer in an interview in the pro-Kurdish newspaper OZGUR GUNDEM, which sent three journalists to interview him at Barr Ilyas in Lebanon. [passage omitted]
